text: Fusinus wallacei is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Fasciolariidae, the spindle snails, the tulip snails and their allies. ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Indonesia ==References== * Hadorn R. & Fraussen K. 2006. Five new species of Fusinus (Gastropoda: Fasciolariidae) from western Pacific and Arafura Sea. Novapex 7(4): 91-102 wallacei Category:Gastropods described in 2006
title: Fusinus wallacei
